> **Music:** All music was composed by jswessler using Ableton Live 12. Find MYMEMORY's OST on Spotify, Apple Music, and YouTube!
> **Sound FX:** Sound effects were created by jswessler and from some free & open source repositories. See a list of sound credits [https://docs.google.com/document/d/1_0H1SGBgjNobPh_8GaSrfAlxdzFUOCdFr3ixfyhWjOw/edit?usp=sharing here].
